OL,3,CKevin Keegan reveals stage four cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis
OL,6,FFormer England and Newcastle manager
OL,7,FKevin Keegan has revealed he has stage
OL,8,Ffour cancer.
OL,10,FKeegan's family revealed in January
OL,11,Fthe former Newcastle and England
OL,12,Fplayer had been diagnosed with cancer,
OL,13,Fbut during an appearance at the Tyne
OL,14,FTheatre and Opera House over the
OL,15,Fweekend, the 75-year-old updated those
OL,16,Fat the event.
OL,18,FKeegan is reported to have said: "They
OL,19,Fsaid we have a top doctor with this
OL,20,Fnew way of fighting what you have got,
OL,21,Fwhich is stage four cancer."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
