PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780517152
OL,3,CKevin Keegan reveals stage four cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis
OL,6,FHe is also believed to have stated he
OL,7,Fwould like to return to St James' Park
OL,8,Fto say goodbye, saying: "I want to say
OL,9,Fgoodbye. I didn't get the chance when
OL,10,FI left the club last time."
OL,12,FNewcastle United Football Club, where
OL,13,FKeegan spent two years as a player
OL,14,Fbefore having two spells as a manager,
OL,15,Fsent their best wishes to Keegan in a
OL,16,Fpost on X today (Monday 1 June).
OL,18,FIt said: "We send our heartfelt
OL,19,Fsupport and warmest wishes to Kevin
OL,20,FKeegan and his family following his
OL,21,Frecent diagnosis of stage four cancer."
OL,26,@pD@YOUrD@[O]zD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
