PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780517152
OL,3,CKevin Keegan reveals stage four cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis
OL,6,F"Kevin holds a unique and cherished
OL,7,Fplace in the history of Newcastle, and
OL,8,Fin the hearts of our supporters. His
OL,9,Fpassion, leadership and connection to
OL,10,Fthe club and city have shaped some of
OL,11,Four most memorable moments.
OL,13,F"Everyone at the club is behind Kevin
OL,14,Fand sends strength and best wishes to
OL,15,Fhim and his family for the journey
OL,16,Fahead.
OL,18,F"Kevin will always be warmly welcomed
OL,19,Fat St James' Park and we hope to see
OL,20,Fhim again soon."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU|D@PO]
