CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780517152
OL,3,CKevin Keegan reveals stage four cancer
OL,4,Cdiagnosis
OL,6,FAs a manager, Keegan took charge of
OL,7,Fformer club Newcastle in 1992 and led
OL,8,Fthem into the Premier League, where
OL,9,Fthey came close to winning the 1995-96
OL,10,Ftitle but missed out to Manchester
OL,11,FUnited.
OL,13,FHe then made a return to Newcastle in
OL,14,F2008, but lasted eight months at the
OL,15,Fhelm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
